thread.title: Jeanette Teague
thread.title_full: Ink Station reviewed by Jeanette Teague

author: Jeanette Teague
title: Jeanette Teague
text: As a first time user of Ink Station and I was very impressed; excellent website where finding the products I needed was easy, had a quick question which was easily answered by competent staff, prices were good and the order was fast - delivered in a few days to regional Victoria. I couldn't fault the experience.
